Title: .NET Framework May 2021 Cumulative Update Preview for Windows 10, versions 2004, 20H2, 21H1 | .NET Blog
Description: Today, we are releasing the May 2021 Cumulative Update Preview for .NET Framework. Quality and Reliability This release contains the following quality and reliability improvements. CLR1 Addresses a performance issue caused by incorrect configuration in the GC. Addresses an issue where a background GC could pause the runtime for a long period of time if a large managed heap is filled with long lived objects with a deep chain of references.
